'''西风带'''，又称'''盛行西风带'''<ref>{{Cite book |title=简明地理辞典 |last=田松庆 |publisher=湖北人民出版社 |year=1984 |pages=485}}</ref>，是[[中纬度|中纬度]]地区（[[纬度|纬度]]在{{deg|35}}－{{deg|65}}之间）自西向东吹的[[盛行风|盛行风]]，由[[副热带高压带|副热带高压带]]的高压区域吹向[[极地|极地]]区域。<ref name="AMS_2009">{{Cite web |title=Westerlies |url=http://amsglossary.allenpress.com/glossary/search?id=westerlies1 |date=2005 |publisher=American Meteorological Society |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100622073904/http://amsglossary.allenpress.com/glossary/search?id=westerlies1 |archive-date=2010-06-22 |website=Glossary of Meteorology |access-date=2018-01-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>北半球的西风带主要吹西南[[风|风]]，南半球则主要吹西北风。当半球处于[[冬季|冬季]]且极地附近的气压较低时，西风带最强；而当半球处于[[夏季|夏季]]且极地附近的气压较高时，西风带最弱。南半球的中纬度地区少有会导致西风减速的陆地，因此盛行西风格外强。西风带中存在着各类[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]和[[反气旋|反气旋]]。越过[[副热带高压脊线|副热带高压脊线]]进入西风带的[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]会因西风的增加而转向，并可能发生[[温带变性|温带变性]]。盛行西风还把温暖的[[赤道|赤道]]水和空气带到中纬度[[大陆|大陆]]的西海岸，对其气候特征起着重要作用。

==成因及影响因素==
由于[[地球|地球]]的不同地区所接收到的太阳辐射能量分布不均匀，温暖的亚热带大气和较冷的极地大气之间存在着温度梯度，这是盛行西风的主要能量来源。<ref name=wen>{{Cite book|chapter=Westerlies, middle-latitude west winds|title=Climatology|url=http://link.springer.com/10.1007/0-387-30749-4_197|publisher=Kluwer Academic Publishers|date=1987|location=Dordrecht|isbn=978-0-87933-009-5|pages=922–928|doi=10.1007/0-387-30749-4_197|language=en|first=Jay R.|last=Harman}}</ref>如果地球被太阳[[潮汐锁定|潮汐锁定]]，中纬度区域的风会吹向极地。然而，由于地球[[自转|自转]]引起的[[科里奥利力|科里奥利力]]，吹向极地的风会向东偏转，对于北半球是右偏，对于南半球是左偏。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Solar Heating and Coriolis Forces |url=http://csep10.phys.utk.edu/astr161/lect/earth/coriolis.html |accessdate=2009-05-31 |last=Gasser |first=Nathan |work=University of Tennessee |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090519040309/http://csep10.phys.utk.edu/astr161/lect/earth/coriolis.html |archive-date=2009-05-19 }}</ref>因此，北半球的西风带主要吹西南风，南半球的西风带则主要吹西北风。<ref>{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=OLMXAAAAIAAJ&pg=PA246&lpg=PA246&dq=direction+of+the+prevailing+westerlies+in+northern+hemisphere+southwest&source=bl&ots=C2SzvUDsje&sig=dkFc55QfdoJhBCygMCVIu9u-4_s&hl=en&ei=5eXlSfzwKIvKMJOUlYQJ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=3 |title=Advanced geography |last=Tarr |first=Ralph |last2=McMurry |first2=Frank |publisher=State Printing |accessdate=2009-04-15 |year=1909 |page=246 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140102060829/http://books.google.com/books?id=OLMXAAAAIAAJ&pg=PA246&lpg=PA246&dq=direction+of+the+prevailing+westerlies+in+northern+hemisphere+southwest&source=bl&ots=C2SzvUDsje&sig=dkFc55QfdoJhBCygMCVIu9u-4_s&hl=en&ei=5eXlSfzwKIvKMJOUlYQJ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=3 |archive-date=2014-01-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

全年来看，盛行西风的强度随着[[极地气旋|极地气旋]]的变化而变化。冬季，随着气旋达到最强，盛行西风增强；夏季，随着气旋达到最弱，盛行西风减弱。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Global circulation |url=http://andvari.vedur.is/~halldor/HB/Met210old/GlobCirc.html |accessdate=2008-06-15 |last=Björnsson |first=Halldór |work=Veðurstofu Íslands |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110807132251/http://andvari.vedur.is/~halldor/HB/Met210old/GlobCirc.html |archivedate=2011-08-07 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>当[[北极涛动|北极涛动]]指数为正时，极地气压较低，盛行西风增强，使得中纬度地区变暖。反之，当北极涛动指数为负时，极地气压较高，盛行西风减弱，结果极地冷空气南下，使中纬度地区变得寒冷。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Patterns in Arctic Weather and Climate {{!}} National Snow and Ice Data Center |url=https://nsidc.org/cryosphere/arctic-meteorology/weather_climate_patterns.html |accessdate=2020-07-14 |author=National Snow and Ice Data Center |work=Arctic Climatology and Meteorology |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200703100801/https://nsidc.org/cryosphere/arctic-meteorology/weather_climate_patterns.html |archive-date=2020-07-03 }}</ref>南半球的中纬度地区少有会导致西风减速的陆地，因此盛行西风格外强。<ref name=geo/>由于其多云、多暴风雨的天气，根据纬度的不同，此区域分别被人们称为[[咆啸40度|咆啸40度]]、[[狂暴50度|狂暴50度]]和[[尖叫60度|尖叫60度]]。<ref>{{Cite book |url=https://archive.org/details/sailorswind00walk |title=The sailor's wind |last=Walker |first=Stuart |publisher=W. W. Norton & Company |year=1998 |isbn=9780393045550 |pages=[https://archive.org/details/sailorswind00walk/page/91 91] |quote=Roaring Forties  Shrieking Sixties  westerlies.}}</ref>其中，西风在处于{{deg|40}}{{cdash}}{{deg|50}}S之间的咆啸40度最强。<ref name=geo>{{Cite web|title=Wind|url=http://www.nationalgeographic.org/encyclopedia/wind/|accessdate=2020-07-17|date=2012-11-15|last=Society|first=National Geographic|work=National Geographic Society|language=en|quote=The strongest westerlies blow through the "Roaring Forties," a wind zone between 40 and 50 degrees latitude in the Southern Hemisphere.|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200613045652/https://www.nationalgeographic.org/encyclopedia/wind/|archive-date=2020-06-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==对洋流的影响==
[[Image:Franklingulfstream.jpg|thumb]]绘制的[[湾流|湾流]]地图]]
在[[大西洋|大西洋]]和[[太平洋|太平洋]]洋面上的副热带高压北侧，存在着自西向东吹的盛行风，驱动着南北两半球的[[洋流|洋流]]以相似的形式流动。<ref>{{Cite journal |title=What Is the Thermohaline Circulation? |url=http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/summary/298/5596/1179 |last=Wunsch |first=Carl |date=November 8, 2002 |journal=Science |issue=5596 |doi=10.1126/science.1079329 |volume=298 |pages=1179–1181 |pmid=12424356 |quote=The upper layers of the ocean are clearly wind-driven, involving such major features as the Gulf Stream and the Circumpolar Current. [...] |access-date=2020-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090925190615/http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/summary/298/5596/1179 |archive-date=2009-09-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=The Thermohaline Ocean Circulation |url=http://www.pik-potsdam.de/~stefan/thc_fact_sheet.html |author=Rahmstorf |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6F180jPsW?url=http://www.pik-potsdam.de/~stefan/thc_fact_sheet.html |archivedate=2013-03-10 |access-date=2020-07-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>盛行西风和信风的作用导致大洋环流的[[西岸强化|西岸强化]]现象，即洋盆西边界的洋流比东边界洋流更强，并向[[极地|极地]]方向输送温暖的热带水。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Investigating the Gulf Stream |url=http://www.science-house.org/nesdis/gulf/background.html |accessdate=2009-05-06 |author=National Environmental Satellite, Data, and Information Service |work=North Carolina State University |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100503013457/http://www.science-house.org/nesdis/gulf/background.html |archivedate=2010-05-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>例如，[[墨西哥湾暖流|墨西哥湾暖流]]，作为[[北大西洋环流|北大西洋环流]]的一部分，促使各种强[[气旋|气旋]]在盛行西风的基础上生成。<ref>{{Cite journal |title=Cold-air cyclogenesis along the Gulf-Stream front: investigation of diabatic impacts on cyclone development, frontal structure, and track |url=https://doi.org/10.1007/s00703-003-0050-y |last=Businger |first=S. |last2=Graziano |first2=T. M. |date=2005-03-01 |journal=Meteorology and Atmospheric Physics |issue=1 |doi=10.1007/s00703-003-0050-y |volume=88 |pages=65–90 |language=en |issn=1436-5065 |last3=Kaplan |first3=M. L. |last4=Rozumalski |first4=R. A.}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=A FIFTY YEAR HISTORY OF SUBTROPICAL CYCLONES |url=http://ams.confex.com/ams/pdfpapers/37402.pdf |accessdate=2008-09-21 |author=David M. Roth |year=2000 |work=American Meteorological Society |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081003102453/http://ams.confex.com/ams/pdfpapers/37402.pdf |archive-date=2008-10-03 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal |title=Cyclogenesis in the deep ocean beneath the Gulf Stream {{!}} Description |author=D. K. Savidge |url=http://cat.inist.fr/?aModele=afficheN&cpsidt=1914578 |journal=Journal of Geophysical Research |accessdate=2008-09-21 |others=J. M. Bane |year=1999 |page=18111-18126 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120811032434/http://cat.inist.fr/?aModele=afficheN&cpsidt=1914578 |archive-date=2012-08-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>与湾流相似的还有[[日本暖流|日本暖流]]，它是西北太平洋的强[[西边界流|西边界流]]。<ref name="EB1911">{{cite EB1911 |wstitle=Kuro Siwo |volume=15 |page=953}}</ref>

在盛行西风的作用下，有些地区的洋流几乎常年都向东运动，称作西风漂流。<ref name="baike">{{Cite book |url=http://h.bkzx.cn/item/237833 |title=西风漂流 |work=中国大百科全书 |publisher=中国大百科全书出版社 |accessdate=2020-07-16 |year=2016 |isbn=978-7-50007-958-3 |edition=第二版}}</ref>在南半球，西风漂流主要指[[南极环流|南极环流]]，它是自西向东环绕南极洲的洋流，在[[南冰洋|南冰洋]]占主导地位，且是最大的洋流，流量约为1.25×10{{sup|8}} m³/s。<ref>{{Cite web |title=The Antarctic CP Current |url=http://oceancurrents.rsmas.miami.edu/southern/antarctic-cp.html |accessdate=2009-04-11 |author=Ryan Smith, Melicie Desflots, Sean White, Arthur J. Mariano, Edward H. Ryan |work=The Cooperative Institute for Marine and Atmospheric Studies |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100614102611/http://oceancurrents.rsmas.miami.edu/southern/antarctic-cp.html |archive-date=2010-06-14 }}</ref>在北半球，西风漂流则包括[[北大西洋洋流|北大西洋洋流]]和[[北太平洋洋流|北太平洋洋流]]。<ref name=baike/>

==与气旋的相互作用==
[[Image:Bill_2009_track.png|thumb]]，[[2009年飓风比尔|飓风比尔]]转向离开美洲海岸，图为其轨迹。]]
西风带的一个重要特征是其中存在着各类[[气旋|气旋]]和[[反气旋|反气旋]]，这是由于西风带本身具有[[斜压性|斜压性]]。<ref name=wen/>盛行西风会自西向东引导[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]，<ref name="AOML FAQ A7" />这是一种[[天气尺度#綜觀尺度|天气尺度]]的斜压性[[低压|低压]]天气系统，既缺乏热带特征也缺乏[[极地|极地]]特征，出现时往往伴随着[[鋒_(氣象)|锋面]]。<ref name="ExtraLessonMillUni">{{Cite web |title=ESCI 241 – Meteorology; Lesson 16 – Extratropical Cyclones |url=http://www.atmos.millersville.edu/~adecaria/ESCI241/esci241_lesson16_cyclones.html |accessdate=2009-05-31 |author=DeCaria |date=2007-05-29 |publisher=Department of Earth Sciences, Millersville University |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070529043715/http://www.atmos.millersville.edu/~adecaria/ESCI241/esci241_lesson16_cyclones.html |archivedate=2007-05-29 |location=Millersville, Pennsylvania |dead-url=no }}</ref>
温带气旋一般在热带以外的行星中纬度地区产生，根据产生地点，温带气旋也被叫做“中纬度气旋”，<ref name="ExtraLessonMillUni" /><ref name="ExtratropicalPhases">{{Cite web |title=Synoptic Composites of the Extratropical Transition Lifecycle of North Atlantic TCs as Defined Within Cyclone Phase Space |url=http://ams.confex.com/ams/pdfpapers/70524.pdf |accessdate=2006-10-03 |year=2003 |dead-url=yes |author1=Robert Hart |author2=Jenni Evans |lastauthoramp=yes |website=ams.confex.com |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110609164448/http://ams.confex.com/ams/pdfpapers/70524.pdf |archive-date=2011-06-09 }}</ref>根据大气压强，气旋也被叫做“低压”。<ref>{{Cite web |title=低压(气旋) |url=http://www.cma.gov.cn/2011qxfw/2011qqxkp/2011qqxsy/201110/t20111027_126352.html |accessdate=2020-07-16 |author=中国气象报社 |date=2009-09-18 |work=中国气象局 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120616090545/http://www.cma.gov.cn/2011qxfw/2011qqxkp/2011qqxsy/201110/t20111027_126352.html |archive-date=2012-06-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>由于温带气旋在存在温度和露点梯度的区域生成，它们绝大多数时候被认为是斜压的，但是温带气旋在它们生命周期的后期有时也可以是[[正压|正压]]的，在此时的气旋四周，温度沿径向的分布相当均匀。<ref>{{Cite web |title=CHAPTER 3: CYCLONE PARADIGMS AND EXTRATROPICAL TRANSITION CONCEPTUALIZATIONS |url=http://www.coaps.fsu.edu/~maue/cyclone_ch3.html |accessdate=2008-06-15 |author=Ryan N. Maue |publisher=Florida State University |pages=2009 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080510210146/http://www.coaps.fsu.edu/~maue/cyclone_ch3.html |archivedate=2008-05-10 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>若温带气旋在温暖的水面上停留并发展出中央垂直对流，则其核心会被温暖，结果其中心区域温度和露点的梯度逐渐减弱，此时温带气旋可能转变为[[亚热带风暴|亚热带风暴]]，并进一步变为[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]。<ref name="AOML FAQ A7">{{Cite web |title=Frequently Asked Questions: What is an extra-tropical cyclone? |url=http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/A7.html |accessdate=2006-07-25 |year=2004 |publisher=[[NOAA|NOAA]] |dead-url=no |author1=Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory |author2=Hurricane Research Division |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070209121005/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/A7.html |archive-date=2007-02-09 }}</ref>温带气旋和反气旋将温度梯度所蕴含的[[势能|势能]]转化成了空气运动的[[动能|动能]]，可以缓解低纬度地区的潜在能量过剩并将之输送至中高纬度地区，有助于防止西风带中斜压的进一步增加。<ref name=wen/>

西风带的斜压和冷空气也会影响热带气旋，而使之逐渐变性为温带气旋，此过程称为“[[溫帶氣旋#與其他氣旋的關係|温带变性]]”。<ref name="ETClimo">{{Cite journal |title=A climatology of extratropical transition of tropical cyclones in the North Atlantic |url=http://journals.ametsoc.org/doi/abs/10.1175/1520-0442%282001%29014%3C0546%3AACOTET%3E2.0.CO%3B2 |date=February 2001 |journal=Journal of Climate |doi=10.1175/1520-0442(2001)014<0546:ACOTET>2.0.CO;2 |pages=546–564 |format=PDF |bibcode=2001JCli...14..546H |author1=Robert E. Hart |author2=Jenni L. Evans |author= |access-date=2020-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170121024528/http://journals.ametsoc.org/doi/abs/10.1175/1520-0442%282001%29014%3C0546%3AACOTET%3E2.0.CO%3B2 |archive-date=2017-01-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>热带气旋往往经由高压区域的破裂处越过[[副热带高压|副热带高压]]脊线，此时受向极地一侧的较低压区域吹去的风的影响，其轨迹会显著偏转，等到变为向极地方向稍偏东移动，气旋进入西风带，并开始转向。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Section 2: Tropical Cyclone Motion Terminology |url=http://www.nrlmry.navy.mil/~chu/chap4/se200.htm |accessdate=2007-04-10 |author=United States Navy |year=2009 |format=iso |work=Joint Typhoon Warning Center |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68e70ZbPt?url=http://www.nrlmry.navy.mil/~chu/chap4/se200.htm |archivedate=2012-06-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>例如在太平洋洋面上生成的向[[亚洲|亚洲]]方向移动的台风，常受[[西风槽|西风槽]]影响而转向离开[[日本|日本]]向北移动，随后向东北移动。<ref>{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=A6gcAQAAIAAJ&q=%E5%8F%B0%E9%A3%8E+%E8%A5%BF%E9%A3%8E%E6%A7%BD |title=海洋学研究 |publisher=海洋出版社 |accessdate=2020-07-14 |year=2007 |editor-last=中国海洋学会, 国家海洋局第二海洋研究所, 浙江省海洋学会 |volume=25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200714162041/https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=A6gcAQAAIAAJ&q=%E5%8F%B0%E9%A3%8E+%E8%A5%BF%E9%A3%8E%E6%A7%BD |archive-date=2020-07-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[2006年台风伊欧凯|2006年台风伊欧凯]]就是一个转向的热带气旋，其轨迹类似。<ref name="CPHC Ioke">{{Cite web |title=Hurricane Ioke: 20–27 August 2006 |url=http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/summaries/2006.php#ioke |accessdate=2007-06-09 |author=Powell, Jeff |date=May 2007 |work=2006 Tropical Cyclones Central North Pacific |publisher=Central Pacific Hurricane Center |dead-url=no |display-authors=etal |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5wfdEOQC3?url=http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/summaries/2006.php#ioke |archive-date=2011-02-21 }}</ref>

==对天气和气候的影响==
中纬度地区的气候受地表和高空的盛行西风支配。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=The Westerlies|url=http://www.jstor.org/stable/212280|last=Hare|first=F. Kenneth|date=1960|journal=Geographical Review|issue=3|doi=10.2307/212280|volume=50|pages=345–367|issn=0016-7428}}</ref>特定位置的日常天气，连同[[表面天气系统|表面天气系统]]，也都在很大程度上受盛行西风的位置和强度的影响。<ref name=encyclo>{{Cite book|chapter=Middle latitude climates|title=Climatology|url=http://link.springer.com/10.1007/0-387-30749-4_116|publisher=Kluwer Academic Publishers|date=1987|location=Dordrecht|isbn=978-0-87933-009-5|pages=581–583|doi=10.1007/0-387-30749-4_116|language=en|first=Allan|last=Perry}}</ref>[[纬向环流指数|纬向环流指数]]衡量西风所占分量，它的变化往往导致中纬度地区气候异常。<ref>{{Cite book|title=Global Climate|author=Boucher, K.|publisher=English University Press|year=1975|isbn=|location=London|pages=|url=http://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Global%20Climate&author=K..%20Boucher&publication_year=1975}}</ref>

在北半球，中纬度地区存在着大量陆地，因此气候的东西差异特别明显。<ref name=encyclo/>盛行西风把温暖的赤道水和空气带到大陆西海岸，<ref>{{Cite web|title=What are the prevailing westerlies?|url=https://www.wfmz.com/weather/what-are-the-prevailing-westerlies/article_747a927b-126f-57f1-95fc-566b0ab2f4d3.html|accessdate=2020-07-17|work=WFMZ.com|language=en}}</ref>使得西海岸地区常常气候温和并有丰富的降水，而在大陆内部则气候的大陆性更强，全年温度[[极差|极差]]更大，降水也更少，且多在夏季。<ref name=encyclo/>根据[[周淑贞气候分类法|周淑贞气候分类法]]，处于纬度{{deg|40}}{{cdash}}{{deg|60}}的中纬度大陆西岸的[[温带海洋性气候|温带海洋性气候]]是全年受西风带影响的气候，而属于[[地中海式气候|地中海式气候]]的纬度{{deg|30}}{{cdash}}{{deg|40}}的中纬度大陆西岸则主要在冬季受西风带影响。<ref>{{Cite book|title=大辞海|last=|first=|publisher=上海辞书出版社|year=2015|isbn=|location=|pages=|url=http://www.dacihai.com.cn/search_index.html?_st=1&keyWord=%E6%B8%A9%E5%B8%A6%E6%B5%B7%E6%B4%8B%E6%80%A7%E6%B0%94%E5%80%99|at=温带海洋性气候|chapter=世界地理卷}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|title=大辞海|last=|first=|publisher=上海辞书出版社|year=2015|isbn=|location=|pages=|url=http://www.dacihai.com.cn/search_index.html?_st=1&keyWord=%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%AD%E6%B5%B7%E5%BC%8F%E6%B0%94%E5%80%99|at=地中海式气候|chapter=天文学地球科学卷}}</ref>

